        <Paragraph>
            Modify your project's HTML template to include the Google <Strong>reCAPTCHA</Strong> JavaScript files. The files you add depend on whether you're working with a WebAssembly or Server project:
        </Paragraph>

        <Paragraph>
            <DocsPageUnorderedList>
                <DocsPageUnorderedListItem>
                    For <Strong>WebAssembly</Strong>, update <Strong>index.html</Strong>.
                </DocsPageUnorderedListItem>
                <DocsPageUnorderedListItem>
